simulation

Class SimulatedBank

  • java.lang.Object
    • simulation.SimulatedBank

  • public class SimulatedBank
extends java.lang.Object
    Simulation of the bank. A set of simulated accounts is initalized at startup.

      • PIN

        private static final int[] PIN
        PIN for each card. (Valid card numbers start with 1)

      • ACCOUNT_NUMBER

        private static final int[][] ACCOUNT_NUMBER
        Array of account numbers associated with each card. For each card, there can be three different types of account, which correspond to the names in class AccountInformation. 0 means no account of this type. (Valid card numbers start with 1)
